::DarkMouse::
She decided to try something else.  She  went around to the front of 
the ship and walked up to the front door. 
"Yo, Any bot in there? I want to talk to you." 
She stood infront of the door, but the shields prevented her from 
walking in.  She knew that if she could only get to Quickstrike, she 
could get things sorted out.  She just had to get to her commander 
and talk to him.
